Barsaum, Lu 'lu '2 , 273- 80.
BSO, I, 1027- 28 (J. Rabbi) .</quote>
               </note>
               <note type="abstract">Jacob of Serug was the Bishop of Serug/Batman. He wrote many poems on biblical and theological topics. He had been a student of the School of Edessa. His relics were transferred to Amida (Diyarbakir) after his death.</note>
